items: Maria , Wife to Don Pedro . Clara , Their Daughter . Guiamara , Wife to Count Alvarez , and Sister to Fernando , disguised like the Mother of the Gipsies , and call'd by the Name of Eugenia . Constanza , Daughter to Fernando , disguis'd like a young Spanish Gipsie , and call'd by the Name of Pretiosa . Christiana , A Gentleman , disguis'd like a Gipsie . Cardochia , A young Hostes to the Gipsies . Servants .
